This placeholder marks the legacy local audit file used only as an explicit migration source:

  data/audit-log.jsonl

The application no longer reads this path. It creates and appends audit-log.jsonl under the external HUMIDORHQ_DATA_ROOT.

Do not commit the live audit log. Do not delete the legacy file until its external copy has been verified.


